data.title: Kick off the month with us at High Frequency Friday as we have another hot one on the books! We have a special edition of Come Together...
data.meta_description:
97 likes, 4 comments - nextlevelatl on October 19, 2023: "Kick off the month with us at High Frequency Friday as we have another hot one on the books! We have a special edition of Come Together with DJ Kemit & Salah Ananse joined by the incomparable Lil John Roberts. In addition, we have the uber talented DeCoteau keeping the lobby on fire. I have a limited number of special pre-sale tickets going on sale this Friday at 10 a.m.! Mark your calendar and check back here on Friday before they sell out! Tickets for members and the public go on sale next Monday, 10/23. Link to special pre-sale tickets will be in our bio on Friday.

#HighFrequencyFriday #highmuseum #atlanta #ComeToghether #decoteau #salahananse #djkemit #liljohnroberts #nextlevel #nextlevelevents #presale".
